# Geographic Quiz App

## Overview

This interactive quiz application focuses on geography, allowing users to test their knowledge of world locations while providing a rich, engaging experience. The app combines educational content with interactive features like maps, text-to-speech, and visual feedback to create an immersive learning environment.

![Geographic Quiz App Screenshot](path/to/screenshot.png)

## Features

### Core Quiz Functionality

- Multiple-choice geography questions with instant feedback
- Progress tracking and scoring system
- Timer with adjustable difficulty levels
- Review of answers at the end with correct/incorrect indicators

### Interactive Map Integration

- Real-time map display showing the location of selected answers
- Visual indicators for correct and incorrect selections
- Zoom and pan functionality to explore the geography around answers

### Accessibility Features

- Text-to-speech narration for questions and answers
- Dark/light theme toggle for different lighting conditions
- Keyboard shortcuts for navigating the quiz

### Learning Enhancements

- Hint system to eliminate incorrect options
- Note-taking capability for each question
- Bookmark system to save difficult questions for later review
- Emoji reactions to express feelings about questions

### User Experience

- Responsive design that works on desktop and mobile devices
- Confetti animations for correct answers
- Toast notifications for important information
- Focus mode to minimize distractions

## How to Use

1. **Start the Quiz**: Open the app and select your difficulty level (Easy, Medium, Hard, or Expert).
2. **Answer Questions**: Read each geography question and select your answer from the multiple-choice options.
3. **Use the Map**: After selecting an answer, the map will display the location, allowing you to see exactly where it is in the world.
4. **Utilize Features**:
   - Click the speaker icon to hear questions and answers read aloud
   - Use the hint button if you're stuck
   - Take notes on questions for future reference
   - Bookmark challenging questions to revisit later
   - Toggle between light and dark themes based on your preference
5. **Review Results**: After completing all questions, review your score and see which questions you answered correctly or incorrectly.

## Technical Details

The Geographic Quiz App is built using:

- HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript for the core functionality
- Leaflet.js for interactive maps
- Web Speech API for text-to-speech capabilities
- LocalStorage for saving user preferences and progress
- FontAwesome for icons
- Responsive design principles for cross-device compatibility

## Installation

No installation required! This is a web-based application that runs in any modern browser.

1. Clone the repository or download the files
2. Open index.html in your web browser
3. Start learning about world geography!

## Future Enhancements

- Additional question categories (capitals, landmarks, rivers, etc.)
- User accounts to save progress across devices
- Leaderboards to compare scores with friends
- Custom quiz creation for teachers and educators
- More detailed information about each location

